Shi-Jie Deng serves as an Assistant Professor at the School of Industrial and Systems Engineering (ISyE), which is located at the esteemed Georgia Institute of Technology. His professional communications can be addressed through his office telephone number, (404) 894-6519. Similarly, electronic correspondence can be sent to deng@isye.gatech.edu. For those seeking additional information, his personal professional platform can be accessed via http://www.isye.gatech.edu/~deng.